    <h1 id='rewiding'>Rewiding</h1>


    <h1 id='rewiding'>Rewiding</h1>

    <p>All land is communally held and rented for short periods. People have access to high quality goods, but own relatively little. Travel is simple and expected. Time commitments are, for the most part, for concrete and relatively short periods.</p>
    <p>Animals are free to roam.</p>

